description.en: Outdoor entertaining area and pool surround in Doncaster with non-slip textured porcelain pavers, screeded drainage falls, expansion joint caulking, weather-resistant grouting, and a tiled built-in barbecue bench.
description.zh: Doncaster户外休闲区和泳池周边，防滑纹理瓷质砖铺设、找平排水坡度、伸缩缝密封、耐候填缝处理，以及瓷砖砌筑烧烤台面。
